TY  - JOUR
TI  - Simultaneous Equations: Any Verdict Yet?
AU  - Hildreth, Clifford
AB  - [This paper offers reasons for believing that experience with applications of existing simultaneous equations procedures does not yet furnish a basis for reliably appraising their practical usefulness. The need to consider simultaneity of relations in conjunction with other sources of specification error is stressed. Prediction with knowledge of some endogenous variables is briefly discussed.]
C1  - Full publication date: Oct., 1960
