TY  - JOUR
TI  - A Dual Stability Theorem
AU  - Jorgenson, Dale W.
AB  - [A dual interpretation of the Leontief dynamic input-output system suggests the problem: What is the relationship between the stability of the output system and the stability of the dual? If the output system is stable, the dual must be unstable and vice versa, at least for the closed system. For the open system the statement is true except under rather implausible circumstances.]
